      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "kosher salt",
      "amount": "pinch"
    },
    {
      "name": "pumpkin puree",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "agave nectar syrup",
      "amount": "2 tablespoons"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a small mixing bowl, combine canola oil, flaxseed meal, and salt. Mix well until no lumps remain.",
    "Add pumpkin puree and agave nectar syrup to the dry ingredients in the mixing bowl. Stir together until a smooth crumble forms.",
    "Transfer the crumble mixture onto an oiled baking sheet. Bake for 12-15 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from oven, let cool slightly before serving."
